msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "已启用"

msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "未启用"

msgid "Cooling active"
msgstr "正在散热"

msgid "Modulating"
msgstr "调速中"

msgid "Standby"
msgstr "待机"

msgid "Unavailable"
msgstr "不可用"

msgid "Sensor unavailable"
msgstr "传感器不可用"

msgid "to start"
msgstr "后启动"

msgid "Full-speed ceiling reached"
msgstr "已达到满速温度上限"

msgid "Save & Apply below to persist changes."
msgstr "需要点击下方的“保存并应用”后，修改才会真正生效。"

msgid "Enable the service and Save & Apply to start the fan daemon."
msgstr "启用服务后，再点击“保存并应用”即可启动风扇守护进程。"

msgid "Loaded into the form"
msgstr "已写入表单"

msgid "Not available"
msgstr "不可用"

msgid "This device needs a readable CPU thermal zone and a writable pwm-fan hwmon interface for the full temperature-driven control loop."
msgstr "当前设备需要可读的 CPU 温区和可写的 PWM 风扇 hwmon 接口，才能使用完整的温度驱动控速。"

msgid "Turbo and Manual modes require a writable pwm-fan hwmon interface on the target board."
msgstr "狂暴模式和手动模式需要目标设备提供可写的 pwm-fan hwmon 接口。"

msgid "Waiting for telemetry..."
msgstr "正在等待遥测数据..."

msgid "Monitoring state"
msgstr "监控状态"

msgid "Current device"
msgstr "当前设备"

msgid "BPI-R4 tuned layout with live CPU temperature, PWM duty, and fan speed feedback across smart, manual and turbo modes."
msgstr "已针对 BPI-R4 优化，实时展示 CPU 温度、PWM 占空比，以及智能、手动、狂暴三种模式下的风扇转速反馈。"

msgid "Live OpenWrt cooling dashboard with a configurable smart temperature window, plus manual and turbo profiles on pwm-fan capable hardware."
msgstr "当目标硬件提供 pwm-fan 能力时，可在这里实时查看 OpenWrt 散热状态，并使用可配置智能温区、手动和狂暴三种模式。"

msgid "Turbo"
msgstr "狂暴"

msgid "Smart"
msgstr "智能"

msgid "Manual"
msgstr "手动"

msgid "Turbo mode locks the fan at the configured full-speed RPM ceiling after Save & Apply."
msgstr "狂暴模式在“保存并应用”后会把风扇锁定在已配置的满速转速上限。"

msgid "Smart mode linearly ramps from the stop temperature to the configured full-speed RPM ceiling."
msgstr "智能模式会在停转温度到满速温度之间线性调速，并遵循已配置的满速转速上限。"

msgid "Manual mode applies the selected duty target after Save & Apply and reports the available fan speed feedback."
msgstr "手动模式会在“保存并应用”后采用所选占空比，并显示当前可用的风扇转速反馈。"

msgid "Mode target"
msgstr "目标模式"

msgid "Current fan duty"
msgstr "当前风扇占空比"

msgid "(estimated)"
msgstr "（估算）"

msgid "(actual)"
msgstr "（真实）"

msgid "PWM speed feedback"
msgstr "PWM 转速反馈"

msgid "Hardware speed feedback"
msgstr "硬件转速反馈"

msgid "Speed feedback unavailable"
msgstr "转速反馈不可用"

msgid "Speed feedback"
msgstr "转速反馈"

msgid "Fan stop below"
msgstr "低于此温度停转"

msgid "Full speed above"
msgstr "高于此温度满速"

msgid "The fan is linearly modulating between the stop floor and the full-speed ceiling."
msgstr "当前风扇正在停转温度和满速温度之间线性调速。"

msgid "Backend control uses the kernel thermal reading directly, so the smart curve tracks temperature changes at 0.1 C granularity."
msgstr "后端直接使用内核热区读数，因此智能曲线按 0.1 摄氏度粒度跟踪温度变化。"

msgid "Adaptive Fan Profile"
msgstr "自适应风扇控制"

msgid "Live Cooling Dashboard"
msgstr "实时散热面板"

msgid "CPU temperature"
msgstr "CPU 温度"

msgid "Fan speed"
msgstr "风扇转速"

msgid "Current PWM duty"
msgstr "当前 PWM 占空比"

msgid "Control mode"
msgstr "控制模式"

msgid "Smart curve"
msgstr "智能曲线"

msgid "Current temperature"
msgstr "当前温度"

msgid "Operating profiles"
msgstr "运行模式"

msgid "Use these shortcuts to load Turbo, Smart or Manual targets into the form below before Save & Apply."
msgstr "可用这些快捷按钮把狂暴、智能或手动目标写入下方表单，然后再执行“保存并应用”。"

msgid "Turbo mode"
msgstr "狂暴模式"

msgid "Smart mode"
msgstr "智能模式"

msgid "Manual mode"
msgstr "手动模式"

msgid "Runtime insight"
msgstr "运行提示"

msgid "Current config"
msgstr "当前设置"

msgid "Enabled in UCI"
msgstr "UCI 启用状态"

msgid "Manual target"
msgstr "手动目标"

msgid "Runtime fan speed"
msgstr "当前风扇转速"

msgid "Fan Control"
msgstr "风扇控制"

msgid "Configure Smart, Turbo and Manual fan profiles for pwm-fan capable boards such as the BPI-R4. The live panel reads CPU temperature, PWM duty, and fan speed feedback over ubus."
msgstr "为 BPI-R4 等支持 pwm-fan 的设备配置智能、狂暴和手动风扇模式。实时面板会通过 ubus 读取 CPU 温度、PWM 占空比，以及风扇转速反馈。"

msgid "Profile Settings"
msgstr "基本设置"

msgid "Enable fan service"
msgstr "启用风扇服务"

msgid "Start the fan daemon on Save & Apply. Smart mode uses the configured temperature window, Turbo holds the configured RPM ceiling, and Manual applies the slider target on pwm-fan capable boards."
msgstr "点击“保存并应用”后会启动风扇守护进程。智能模式会按已配置的温度区间调速，狂暴模式固定在已配置的满速转速上限，手动模式会在支持 pwm-fan 的设备上应用滑条目标。"

msgid "Smart mode follows the configured stop and full-speed temperatures. Turbo and Manual require pwm-fan hwmon support on the target board."
msgstr "智能模式会按已配置的停转温度和满速温度调速。狂暴模式和手动模式需要目标设备提供 pwm-fan hwmon 支持。"

msgid "Temperature in C below which the smart profile stops the fan. You can customize when the fan starts to stay off."
msgstr "智能模式下低于该温度时风扇停转，可自定义风扇开始保持关闭的温度。"

msgid "Temperature in C at which smart mode reaches the configured RPM ceiling."
msgstr "智能模式下达到该温度时会拉到已配置的满速转速上限。"

msgid "Maximum fan RPM"
msgstr "风扇最大转速"

msgid "Display and estimation ceiling for fan speed. Set values such as 2500, 3000 or 3500 to match your hardware."
msgstr "风扇转速的显示和估算上限。可设置为 2500、3000 或 3500 等数值，以匹配你的风扇。"

msgid "Manual PWM target"
msgstr "手动 PWM 目标"

msgid "Duty target in percent for Manual mode. 0 turns the fan off, 100 drives the maximum PWM value, which maps to the configured RPM ceiling in the display."
msgstr "手动模式下的目标占空比，单位为百分比。0 表示关闭风扇，100 表示输出最大 PWM，对应页面显示中已配置的转速上限。"

msgid "Polling interval"
msgstr "轮询间隔"

msgid "Fan daemon loop interval in seconds. The default 5-second cadence is usually enough for the configurable smart curve and reduces unnecessary PWM writes."
msgstr "风扇守护进程的轮询间隔，单位为秒。默认 5 秒通常已足够匹配可配置智能曲线，并可减少无意义的 PWM 写入。"